    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of MarkupSafe</title>

      <para>
        Install <application>MarkupSafe</application> with the following
        commands:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        Then, as the &root; user:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir markupsafe</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

